Area 3 of  Ukiah Christmas Bird Count.  Two parties:  Barbara Dolan and John Dane worked north from the south end of the dam to Miti Campground. A second party of Roger Foote, Geoff Heinecken, Greg Cox, and George Chaniot worked south from the inlet to Miti Campground to meet up with the other party.--     06:30 - 15:00  My party covered the area from the inlet south to the barn.  Dreadful heavy rain, high wind from the south.  Everyone got wet.   Mercifully, during the day the temperature was not too cold, Creeka and Lake Mendocino were visably rising.   Had lunch at the barn and decided to head back.  Quit about 13:30.  Drove to Oak Grove parking lot and scoped the Pomo Area with Roger Foote.  It's a good thing we did this because Ollie's team quit at 09:30 and didn't cover it.
